 message them Expected Results: 20-30 property responses within 48 hours 5-8 video tours arranged within 1 week Shortlist of 8-12 viable properties within 2 weeks The Humphreys' property proves that $1,500/month all-inclusive villa living in Hua Hin is absolutely achievable. Similar properties in the 45,000-55,000 THB range are currently available. Your success depends on starting early, building relationships with agents, and being financially prepared for deposits. The exact property type you want is out there - this action plan will help you find it! 🏝️🏠 Super Agent Genspark Claw Free Now +13 Ultra Speak"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=9ce745cd-8e96-44c4-9fc1-f831ed9465c2","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=9ce745cd-8e96-44c4-9fc1-f831ed9465c2"}]}]}]
